    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><script class="meting-secondary-script-marker" src="\assets\js\Meting.min.js"></script><h3 id="记录博客的搭建工作"><a href="#记录博客的搭建工作" class="headerlink" title="记录博客的搭建工作"></a>记录博客的搭建工作</h3><blockquote><h5 id="基本工作如下："><a href="#基本工作如下：" class="headerlink" title="基本工作如下："></a>基本工作如下：</h5><ul><li><p>配置环境</p></li><li><p>搭建博客</p></li><li><p>美化博客</p><p><em>Everything</em> is accoring to <em><strong>plan</strong></em>!</p></li></ul></blockquote><span id="more"></span><h4 id="环境配置"><a href="#环境配置" class="headerlink" title="环境配置"></a>环境配置</h4><ol><li>安装nodeJS</li><li>安装Git</li><li>安装Hexo</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>​    在以下安装版本查看确认无误后，则可以进行接下来的工作：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br><span class="line">git --version</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>以下是本机版本信息：</p><p><img src="https://s1.328888.xyz/2022/05/29/tx8TT.png" alt="tx8TT.png"></p><h4 id="搭建博客"><a href="#搭建博客" class="headerlink" title="搭建博客"></a>搭建博客</h4><ol><li>去<a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>创建仓库，仓库名同自己的<strong>用户注册名</strong>（wtastme.github.io）</li><li>生成密钥，完成绑定</li></ol><ul><li><p>生成SSH Key</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh-keygen -t rsa -C <span class="string">&quot;xxx@xxx.com&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>获取密钥，进行绑定</p></li></ul><p>​    在系统盘下的**.ssh<strong>文件夹中，打开</strong>id_rsa.pub<strong>，将其内容完整的粘贴到<a href="https://github.com/">GitHub</a>的</strong>SSH and GPG keys**中</p><ul><li><p>验证是否绑定成功</p>  <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">ssh -T git@github.com</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><p>​    若出现Hi…，Successfully authenticated则表示绑定完成</p><ol start="3"><li><p>添加Git全局范围的用户名及邮箱</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global user.email wtastme@163.com</span><br><span class="line">git config --global user.name wtastme</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若配置错误，可以删除后重新配置</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --<span class="built_in">unset</span> user.name</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --<span class="built_in">unset</span> user.email</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>若遇见报错：“unsafe repository…指向一个本地路径”，则将其添加为安全目录即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --add safe.directory <span class="string">&quot;*&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>初始化Hexo博客，并安装部署工具</p> <figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo init blog</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">5. 配置文件修改</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">​对blog 根目录下的**_config.yml**文件修改</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```bash</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">type</span>: git</span><br><span class="line">  repository: https://github.com/Wtastme/Wtastme.github.io.git</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><blockquote><p>注： 若仓库分支名为<strong>main</strong>就写<strong>main</strong>，若为<strong>master</strong>则为<strong>master</strong></p></blockquote><ol start="6"><li>生成博客，并远端部署</li></ol><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>注： 在hexo d的过程中，首次会要求登录，根据现版本GitHub的更新要求进行验证即可</p></blockquote><h4 id="美化博客"><a href="#美化博客" class="headerlink" title="美化博客"></a>美化博客</h4><p>​    持续更新中…</p>]]></content>
    
    
